---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Nestey">
  <NavBar />

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <p class="lead">
          Nestey was born from a simple belief:<br /><strong
            >work should feel human.</strong
          >
        </p>

        <p>
          For years, I led large transformation programs and watched employees
          struggle with systems that were supposed to help them. People were
          overwhelmed by benefits they didn't understand, lost in HR portals
          that felt like relics, and unsure where to turn for clear answers.
          Even the most capable employees often felt alone navigating decisions
          that impact their careers, finances, health, and families.
        </p>

        <p>I knew there had to be a better way.</p>

        <p>
          Nestey started as a personal mission — a desire to build something
          that felt warm, intuitive, and genuinely supportive. A tool built for
          people, not processes. A modern HR experience that answers real
          questions in real time, the way a trusted advisor would.
        </p>

        <p class="emphasis">But Nestey became more than that.</p>

        <div class="highlight-section">
          <p>It became a place where technology meets empathy.</p>
          <p>
            Where employees can simply ask, "What should I do next?" and get
            clear, personalized guidance.
          </p>
          <p>Where HR teams can focus on people instead of processes.</p>
          <p>
            Where every interaction feels effortless — like talking to someone
            who already understands your world.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="emphasis">
          Nestey is designed to be the HR experience we all wish existed:
        </p>

        <ul class="values-list">
          <li>conversational</li>
          <li>intelligent</li>
          <li>proactive</li>
          <li>deeply personalized</li>
          <li>and beautifully simple</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          It helps employees make confident decisions about their time off,
          benefits, goals, performance, and career. And it gives organizations a
          modern platform that finally brings clarity, consistency, and calm to
          the HR ecosystem.
        </p>

        <p>
          I didn't build Nestey to compete with anyone.<br />
          I built it because employees deserve better — and because the future of
          work demands tools that lift people up instead of wearing them down.
        </p>

        <div class="closing-section">
          <p>Nestey is your workplace companion.</p>
          <p>Your guide.</p>
          <p>Your "what's next" coach.</p>
          <p>Your safe place to ask anything.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="emphasis">
          This is HR, reimagined for the world we live in today — and the one
          we're building tomorrow.
        </p>

        <p class="welcome">Welcome to Nestey.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    background: var(--brand-background);
    padding: 5rem 0 6rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--brand-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 2.5rem !important;
    line-height: 1.3 !important;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem !important;
    color: var(--brand-blue) !important;
  }

  .lead strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .emphasis {
    font-size: 1.25rem !important;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--brand-blue) !important;
    margin-top: 2.5rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
  }

  .highlight-section {
    background: white;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-blue);
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .highlight-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--brand-blue);
  }

  .highlight-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 2rem;
  }

  .values-list li {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--brand-blue);
    font-weight: 500;
    position: relative;
  }

  .values-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.5rem;
    color: var(--brand-blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .closing-section {
    background: white;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-blue);
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .closing-section p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--brand-blue);
  }

  .closing-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .welcome {
    font-size: 1.5rem !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    color: var(--brand-blue) !important;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem !important;
    }

    .content-wrapper p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .highlight-section,
    .closing-section {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .values-list {
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
